{"tid":2510244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大醫生張貼「武漢肺炎」標語 遭中國新移民議員聲討","createTime":"2021-04-30T04:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T22:15:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":214,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"f9cd118d61d4fd840d21ccb62a33daf201532007","tid":2510244,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"加拿大多倫多一名華人醫生江永家（Kester Kong），被指在醫務所門外，張貼用中文寫上「武漢肺炎」的字眼，遭到安大略省議會、來自中國泉州的新移民議員柯文彬（Vincent Ke）和白必勤（Aris Babikian）聲討，要求他清除標語，以免挑起仇亞情緒。<br />\n<br />\n安大略進步保守黨議員柯文彬，透過電郵向加拿大《國家郵報》表示，如果江永家醫生理解使用「武漢肺炎」一詞，可以「分裂和損害加拿大華人社區」，他便應該把該字眼移除，「無論是口述或書面語，使用『武漢肺炎』一詞來形容COVID-19都是錯誤，而且具有煽動性。事實上，這讓許多加拿大華人感到冒犯。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210430/EIWBPPZ3DJHLZHF7SS2YTM3Z44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210430%2FEIWBPPZ3DJHLZHF7SS2YTM3Z44%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=66dfca0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210430%2FEIWBPPZ3DJHLZHF7SS2YTM3Z44%2F&h=6bc316af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210430/EIWBPPZ3DJHLZHF7SS2YTM3Z44/</a>"},{"pid":"8efb65226988c09832056ff8629bf7756baf2006","tid":2510244,"uid":66324,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"D小粉紅自動蒲頭唔駛煩起佢地底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e305f578ac9fc6498180a7d329e21488fb1442ef","tid":2510244,"uid":253016,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"不愧係支那大<br />\n支那豬旁邊坐住兩個鬼佬助陣幾有氣勢<br />\n牛逼"},{"pid":"227e258f975bf00a41e5ce732480b613bc1eb41c","tid":2510244,"uid":130695,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"加拿大唔係中国省左好耐咩"},{"pid":"cd39c33d6895fa4a67ca16f3a24c9e51566cd8a9","tid":2510244,"uid":66324,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedB